#

Apple and Cranberry Stuffing

45 min
$10
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

EasyQuickComfort Food

Description

A delightful blend of sweet apples and tart cranberries in a warm, savory stuffing that's perfect for any meal.

Ingredients

  • bread cubes: 4 cups
  • dried cranberries: 1 cup
  • apple, diced: 1 medium
  • onion, chopped: 1 medium
  • celery, chopped: 1 cup
  • chicken or vegetable broth: 2 cups
  • butter: 1/2 cup
  • sage: 1 tsp
  • thyme: 1 tsp
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
